This is such a sweet game ;-;
The art is absolutely beautiful and oh the endings - they were so good -> the bad ending was so painful :(( All of the endings are worth getting imo, they're all really cool (oh the feels, even the good endings are emotional </3 /pos), it's not that long of a game and you can keep going back to right before where the ending is decided so it's not that difficult to do - you get the full story that way.
Also, Grim is just the sweetest and I love him :]]]
